# behind authenticated mutation, so practical exposure is bounded. Drop this
# entry once multer >=2.1.2 ships, or earlier if upstream backports.
CVE-2026-3304
CVE-2026-3520

# picomatch ReDoS via crafted extglob patterns. The published 2.x line has
# no fix (latest is 2.3.1; advertised 2.3.2 is not on npm). Fix exists in 3.x
# and 4.x but those are breaking releases consumed transitively by chokidar
# and glob; forcing them via `overrides` regressed several @nestjs/* peers
# locally. The vulnerable code path is glob expansion at build/dev time only,
# never on a request hot path. Drop once chokidar updates or 2.3.2 ships.
CVE-2026-33671
